        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="E0HWw_Jm2xrX7lJcNsn0-13" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;Luego de hacer build con docker...&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;1) Levantamos servidor HTTP en port(8080)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;2) Instanciamos configuracion de Base de Datos&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;3) Inicializamos Base de datos con configuracion&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;4) Configuramos Filtros&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;5) Registro de Rutas para comportamiento API REST de nuestra App&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Conceptos importantes:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;HTTP:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-subtree=&quot;aimfl,mfl&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot;&gt;Una solicitud HTTP (HTTP Request) es un &lt;/span&gt;&lt;mark class=&quot;HxTRcb&quot; data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-wiz-uids=&quot;dGbr2_8&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-ved=&quot;2ahUKEwig5c7or7aUAxVWrpUCHTKZHkYQuJAPegoIAggACAAIARAD&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(238, 240, 255);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(238, 240, 255);&quot;&gt;mensaje enviado por un cliente (como un navegador web o aplicación móvil) a un servidor para solicitar una acción, como obtener, crear o actualizar datos&lt;/mark&gt;. Es la base de la comunicación en la web, utilizando métodos (GET, POST, etc.) para interactuar con recursos&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Endpoints:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-subtree=&quot;aimfl,mfl&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot;&gt;Un &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-wiz-uids=&quot;as49dc_8&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot;&gt;endpoint&lt;/span&gt; en el backend &lt;mark class=&quot;HxTRcb&quot; data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-wiz-uids=&quot;as49dc_a&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-ved=&quot;2ahUKEwjDjo7LtraUAxX8LrkGHeCdFfwQuJAPegoIAggACAAIARAD&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(238, 240, 255);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(238, 240, 255);&quot;&gt;es una URL específica (ruta) dentro de una API donde el servidor recibe peticiones y envía respuestas de datos&lt;/mark&gt; (usualmente en formato JSON). Actúa como el punto de acceso final para interactuar con recursos específicos, como &lt;code dir=&quot;ltr&quot; class=&quot;KDcb0c&quot; data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0.909091px solid rgb(44, 46, 53);&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0.909091px solid rgb(44, 46, 53);&quot;&gt;/user/new&lt;/code&gt;&amp;nbsp;para gestionar usuarios, utilizando métodos HTTP (GET, POST, etc.)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Métodos API REST:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-subtree=&quot;aimfl,mfl&quot; data-processed=&quot;true&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot; style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255)); font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(230, 232, 240);&quot;&gt;Son &lt;/span&gt;&lt;mark class=&quot;HxTRcb&quot; data-sfc-root=&quot;c&quot; data-wiz-uids=&quot;q4nHef_g&quot; data-sfc-cb=&quot;&quot; data-ved=&quot;2ahUKEwiwk_GDt7aUAxXzK7kGHRbHFs0QuJAPegoIAggACAAIBxAB&quot; data-processed=&quot;true&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px rgb(238, 240, 255);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; border-bottom: 0px rgb(238, 240, 255);&quot;&gt;verbos HTTP estándar que definen la acción a realizar sobre un recurso en un servidor, permitiendo operaciones CRUD (Crear, Leer, Actualizar, Borrar).&lt;/mark&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 25px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;Ver Metodos en&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;https://restfulapi.net/http-methods/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="515" width="1232" x="-631.5" y="-360" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
